events.name: Boise State Broncos at Michigan State Spartans

headlines.description: Le'Veon Bell ran for a career-high 210 yards and two touchdowns, including the game-winner with 8:12 remaining in No. 13 Michigan State's 17-13 victory over No. 24 Boise State on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 13 Michigan St. tops Boise St.

events.name: San Jose State Spartans at Stanford Cardinal

headlines.description: Jordan Williamson kicked a career-long 46-yard field goal and the go-ahead score from 20 yards, and No. 21 Stanford survived a 20-17 win over San Jose State on Friday night in its first game since Andrew Luck left.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 21 Stanford edges San Jose St.

headlines.description: Matt Brown ran for 141 yards and a long score, Chris Coyer had a touchdown passing and rushing, and Temple beat Villanova 41-10 on Friday night in its first game since returning to the Big East.
headlines.shortLinkText: Temple returns to Big East with rout of Villanova

events.name: NC State Wolfpack at Tennessee Volunteers

headlines.description: Cordarrelle Patterson scored two first-quarter touchdowns -- one a 41-yard catch, the second a 67-yard run -- and Tennessee beat North Carolina State 35-21 on Friday night in the opening game for both teams.
headlines.shortLinkText: Patterson helps Vols down NC St.

events.name: Wagner Seahawks at Florida Atlantic Owls
